For those of you who watch this channel a lot you know that for quite some time we have been covering the drama between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. When we last left you Jason Momoa was defending Ambers role in Aquaman 2 and Johnny Depp had lost his libel case to the UK newspaper the Sun. However today Depp's lawyers say he is appealing this ruling in the high court.
